To ensure that the babel daemon functions properly, it is necessary to start the simulation first, as this will open the TAP interfaces and assign IPv6 link local addresses.

You can check that the babeld daemon works by looking for UDP packets
sent to port 6696.

The CAP_SYS_ADMIN privilege is required for using network namespaces in INET.
Make sure to read the README file in the showcases/emulation directory for more information.
